{"tid":528493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本推SM健身房　女王當教練做射精管理","createTime":"2018-01-13T23:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T18:42:19.000Z","uid":72009,"like":114,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"29afe1a907f62a12f4234a66bb35cea23f77c28c","tid":528493,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T23:44:01.000Z","msg":"日本去年有業者開設特別的「SM健身房」，訓練師化身成SM女王做個人指導，另外男性射精會降低睪固酮消耗能量，不容易練出肌肉，所以也會進行一周最多射一次的射精管理。<br />\n據《itmedia》報導，日本東京惠比壽、新宿地區，有間相當特別的「SM健身房」，該健身房採用相當隱密的預約制，需要到官方網站預約後才會通知上課地點，進場健身教練會身穿SM女王裝等你，而顧客則需要入境隨俗穿奴隸裝，並且女王會拿繩子幫你「龜甲縛」，這些SM女王全部都有專業的健身技術，所以不用擔心健身方式是否有錯，店經理古川真指出，「公司會實施1到2個月健身課程後才讓女王上工，這些課程都是專業健身員進行指導」。<br />\n實際進行推舉槓鈴時，女王會坐在旁邊進行指導，每做一次後就會用鞭子打一次激勵，古川真：「這樣做的理由是讓男性產生性興奮，分泌賀爾蒙增強肌肉，促進鍛鍊效果」，不過報導指出，SM跟健身融合是否有效果，目前似乎還沒有科學上的根據。<br />\n另外健身房也會根據顧客的M度，來調整鍛鍊的內容，像是3P、跟口頭責罵的特別服務等等。古川真表示，「SM健身房」目前主要的客層為30到50歲的男性，男女比部分則是男性8成、女性2成，健身房內鞭子、蠟燭、乳頭夾、項圈等應有竟有，光鞭子種類就有4、5種，可以根據客人的接受程度選擇。<br />\n古川真也說，除了健身房課程外，也會對顧客的日常生活進行管理，例如就會對奴隸們做射精管理，因為男性射精會降低睪固酮消耗能量，不容易練出肌肉，顧客願意的話，也會幫他們裝貞操帶來限制。飲食方面也會用LINE進行只到，每天不能超過設定好的卡路里。<br />\n到「SM健身房」鍛鍊的顧客表示，「之前上健身房的經驗，但都去3、4次就放棄了，不過這個健身房卻讓我一直想來，這次已經來第7、8次了，體脂肪也從17%降到10%，效果相當好」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180113/640_a25fcaafb6afa531987686b16b3e446d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180113%2F640_a25fcaafb6afa531987686b16b3e446d.jpg&h=268c8ba1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180113/640_03b5a0b8d8e49e0fe0a3e34cc15d1522.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180113%2F640_03b5a0b8d8e49e0fe0a3e34cc15d1522.jpg&h=24cf2f44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180113/640_52d3816d0384d999a1d14926edb87a5f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180113%2F640_52d3816d0384d999a1d14926edb87a5f.jpg&h=f8bf165e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180113/640_a319394783cb0f289396f35c9240157c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180113%2F640_a319394783cb0f289396f35c9240157c.jpg&h=af994f10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/hot/realtime/20180113/1278097\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fhot%2Frealtime%2F20180113%2F1278097&d=JmjKm%2FXIeRW2n9jwsKbyymi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=42142f4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fhot%2Frealtime%2F20180113%2F1278097&h=b2953386\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/hot/realtime/20180113/1278097</a>"},{"pid":"8482d20897654fb19b8431307a5908ee4c3ad9b0","tid":528493,"uid":818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T23:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0456ef78c945ab58a1640a49ea002625a5348ac9","tid":528493,"uid":22694,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T23:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4b2e87912b8a12c6162dfa0833156626c796bd","tid":528493,"uid":3109,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T23:56:49.000Z","msg":"召喚蓋清<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fe7b80fbe2b5814578f288304b7924e6a18dc38","tid":528493,"uid":17103,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T00:13:45.000Z","msg":"有無女版假鳩健生單車 .. 班男既脂肪率應該暴跌"},{"pid":"76317268029dfbb3e7547842d01a36534a3299fa","tid":528493,"uid":63154,"